he tidal disruption is possible for $M\n< 10^{9}M_{\\odot}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Sep 2005 18:18:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2005 18:52:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
