 ZAMS stars,\npresence of deeply embedded sources and lower value of L/M for the cloud,\nsupport the youth of IRAS 19110+1045 vis-a-vis its neighbour, IRAS 19111+1048,\nconsistent with earlier studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2005 06:19:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-30"}
