n 1 Mpc/h is strongest for\ndisk-dominated galaxies with C<2.6. This demonstrates that different processes\nare required to explain environmental trends in the structure and in star\nformation history of galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2005 08:15:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 11 Feb 2006 15:15:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 19 Apr 2006 14:21:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-25"}
